    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against a required level of 3, reflecting the single quasi-static loading condition; this gap is accepted given the static-only submission scope and is documented as a known limitation of the validation campaign. All three QoIs satisfy quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96; percent difference < 10%). The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level for this Class II device submission.",
